description.1:
Why Verifone

For more than 30 years VeriFone has established a remarkable record of leadership in the electronic payment technology industry. VeriFone has one of the leading electronic payment solutions brands and is one of the largest providers of electronic payment systems worldwide.

VeriFone has a diverse, dynamic, and fast-paced work environment in which employees are focused on results and have opportunities to excel. We take pride in the fact that we work with the best and brightest in our industry around the globe. Our competitive fierceness is fed by our passion for excellence in our products and services, and our obsession with customer satisfaction. Across the globe, VeriFone employees are leading the payments industry through experience, innovation, and an entrepreneurial spirit. Whether it’s developing the next platform of secure payment systems or searching for new ways to bring electronic payments to new markets, the team at VeriFone is dedicated to the success of our customers, partners, and investors. It's this passion for innovation that drives each one of our employees to personal and professional success.

What you'll do
Position Summary:

Seek a senior hardware engineer to perform board-level circuit design and development, including digital, analog, and power system management technologies. Determine design approaches and parameters. Conduct experimental tests and analyze operating data to contribute to the development schedule.

Essential Duties and Responsibilities:

• Perform board-level circuit design and development, including digital, analog, and/or system power portions. 
• Responsible for parts selection, schematic capture, and BOM maintenance. 
• Responsible for the design and development of new products as well as the support and modification of existing products. 
• Documentation of design files and theory of operation. 
• Board level debug and field returned failure analysis.
• EMC debug to comply with CE/FCC standard. 
• May lead development projects.

What qualifications will you need to be successful?
Knowledge & Experience:

• Preferred master's degree in Electrical Engineering in a related field with 4 or more years of a hardware design engineer. 
• Knowledge of embedded system design and hardware components such as Signal Integrity design and validation, ARM-based chipsets, Touch Screen display, System Power design, especially with analog circuit design ability. 
• Understanding of various communication channels, including but not limited to RS232, USB, Ethernet, SPI, I2C, I2S, and SDIO. 
• System design with ARM CPU and related interfacing. 
• Experience designing cost-effective PCBA's for embedded systems products. 
• Good verbal and written communications skills. 
• Ability to effectively handle multiple tasks. 
• Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, including failure analysis.

Our commitment

Verifone is committed to creating a diverse environment and is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, gender, gender, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, national origin, genetics, disability, age, or veteran status. Verifone is also committed to compliance with all fair employment practices regarding citizenship and immigration status.

We are looking forward to building a team of Sr. and Jr. Embedded SW Engineer to execute complete embedded software development life cycle. The goal is to create scalable and optimized system solution with our MCU/DSP/ADC IP.

College graduates with related field are welcome!!!

We offer 14 months guaranteed pay with Health and Labour insurance. Company stocks and many more! Come and join us! 

Embedded Software Engineer responsibilities include:
• Designing and implementing software of embedded devices and systems
• Designing, developing, coding, testing and debugging system software
• Analyzing and enhancing efficiency, stability and scalability of system resources


Responsibilities
• Design and implement software of embedded devices and systems from requirements to production and commercial deployment
• Design, develop, code, test and debug system software
• Review code and design
• Analyze and enhance efficiency, stability and scalability of system resources
• Integrate and validate new product designs
• Support software QA and optimize I/O performance
• Provide post production support
• Interface with hardware design and development
• Assess third party and open source software

Requirements
• Proven working experience in software engineering
• BS degree in Computer Science or Engineering
• Experience in hands-on development and troubleshooting on embedded 
targets
• Solid programming experience in C or C++
• Proven experience in embedded systems design with preemptive, multitasking real-time operating systems
• Familiarity with software configuration management tools, defect tracking tools, and peer review
• Excellent knowledge of OS coding techniques, IP protocols, interfaces and hardware subsystems
• Adequate knowledge of reading schematics and data sheets for components
• Strong documentation, writing  and communication skills

【About the Role】
As a Customer Service Representative, you will be participating in customer service training programs and being led by senior colleagues to accumulate practical experience. You will assist the company in observing the behaviors and feedbacks of teachers and students on the platform, patiently putting yourself in customer's position to communicate and convey the core values of AmazingTalker.
The customer service team has to process hundreds of and thousands of messages every day, so you will need to prioritize your to-dos to properly arrange limited resources and time. At the same time, you will also need to have a keen sense of observation in order to find the problem in the user's narrative. In addition, you will use data analysis to collect user feedback, cooperate with the product optimization team, make suggestions, conduct research and implement, ultimately optimizing the product to fundamentally solve the user's problem. Most importantly, you will also need to optimize existing processes and establish standard operation procedures, so that repetitive tasks can be completed in a more efficient manner.

The Customer Service Representative of AmazingTalker is a position full of mission. If you yearn for the interaction between people, enjoy the sense of achievement through solving problems for users, and embrace new challenges in the work, we welcome you to join us and become a part of AmazingTalker!

【熱血團隊】
域動Data Team是由一群對『數據分析』及『AI應用』具有研究及開發熱誠的成員所組成。在這裡你可以接觸到大量即時的使用者行為資料，並將資料科學模型應用於:
『網路廣告投放優化』
『網路用戶辨識』
『消費者行為分析』
我們更致力於尋找優化方案，改善產品體驗設計及為商業決策提供數據支持，提升效率和價值。我們鼓勵組員多方嘗試、思考、展現天馬行空的創意，且能清楚闡述想法，付諸實踐。 ٩(⚙ᴗ⚙)۶

【環境氛圍】

description.20:
Isobar做為數位轉型與數位創新的領導品牌，領先市場佈局打造專業的CR-Marketing顧問諮詢團隊，集結了橫跨數據科學與數位創意的全腦競爭人才，面對高速演化的商業競爭市場，Isobar CR-Marketing顧問團隊扮演數據、創意與策略之間的關鍵轉譯角色，協助品牌透過自身的會員數據來優化CRM操作策略，累積會員數據資產、創造會員數據變現的新商業成長曲線。

在不斷研發創新演算與整合服務的同時，Isobar長期延攬跨界頂尖人才，持續優化團隊並擴大CRM顧問服務的差異化優勢。身為Isobar CR-Marketing團隊的數據科學家，主要的任務是要將品牌核心商業數據透過演算、模型轉化為商業決策的洞察，與CRM商業諮詢顧問共同擬定CRM作業策略建議以及建立具體行動方案。
我們在找一個具備跨界思考能力的新數據力專業人才，貫穿商業思維、數據演算與行銷策略，徹底融入品牌營運的顧問服務，攜手打造數位轉型時代的新顧問服務模式。


Job Responsibilities:
•	研究跨產業會員關鍵價值行為模式，協助團隊提供客戶在CRM經營策略的建議
•	依據不同商業主題，建立分析或預測模型(含研究方法)以應用於CRM操作優化
•	定期協助諮詢顧問製作並優化顧問分析報告：CRM維運追蹤、活動成效⋯等
•	協助維護、優化既有的CRM會員現況診斷分析流程
•	配合客戶需求，提供特定商業與消費會員數據議題的研究分析報告以持續優化決策品質

Job Requirement:
•	熟悉R語言與相關套件(tidyverse、lubridate、caret)
•	5年以上的數據分析、應用、建模的經驗
•	至少3個從數據擷取、數據整理、數據分析、數據建模到商業洞察的完整專案執行實務經驗
•	數理統計模型(Regression、Clustering、Segmentation⋯等)的應用經驗

description.92:
Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.
Corning succeeds through sustained investment in R&D, a unique combination of material and process innovation, and close collaboration with customers to solve tough technology challenges.
Corning’s Display Technologies segment manufactures glass substrates for active matrix liquid crystal displays (“LCDs”) that are used primarily in LCD televisions, notebook computers and flat panel desktop monitors.

Scope of Position:
We are offering a unique job opportunity to conduct cutting-edge research in an exciting field of NLP (English). This job provides a wide range of opportunities to invent and to bring fruition to new life-changing technologies with NLP machine/deep learning (ML/DL) capability.

The successful candidate will
• Work from the Corning Research Center Taiwan located inside ITRI (Industrial Technology Research Institute) in Hsinchu and closely interact with other Corning R&D teams around the globe
• Provide technical leadership for research projects and activities focusing on NLP to support Corning RD&E
• Require proven hands-on experience training and optimizing models, building production-ready inference pipelines in Python
• Guide efforts for developing novel NLP models for Corning businesses
• Play a leading role in creation of relevant IP to protect key inventions related to novel solutions

Day to Day Responsibilities:
• Propose and lead research activities involving NLP evaluation and customization for different applications across Corning businesses; be responsible to understand problems from the customer's point of view and translate into NLP solution and work plans
• Collaborate with internal customers across Corning organizations, design and perform model validation and testing, communicate technical practices and results to internal customers
• Share and contribute Corning’s NLP community of practice in developing the capabilities and promoting areas of applications
• Release and maintain developed code for research and creative tools
• Around 15% global travel is expected

description.127:
大數據分析已成為企業競爭力的重要關鍵之一，其中人工智慧(Artificial Intelligence)被視為是翻轉產業的革命型技術。台達電子為了加速產業界導入AI應用，創造智慧化的加值服務，整合AI相關技術與培訓資源，因而成立AI創新中心(AI Center of Excellence)。 
因應瞬息萬變的商業環境，共享與協作才能快速創新，這是AI創新中心在資源及服務上的定位，台達將透過此中心的資源來培訓人才並與各事業單位合作，落實AI技術於各式服務。

本職缺主要工作內容:
1.	以統計、訊號處理、機器學習與深度學習等技術，透過內外部客戶建立合適的分析診斷解決方案
2.	研究與開發人工智慧之演算法、應用和服務
3.	設計、協助及管理資料分析及最佳化專案、培訓等業務推動
4.	參與智慧製造、智慧生活、智慧企業等產業轉型專案，並設計開發分析流程(含資料採集、邊緣運算分流、演算法選用等)。

你/妳將會應用資料分析技術於以下兩大類別問題
1.	Video & Image Processing and Analytics
	缺陷檢測
	缺陷分類
2.	Time Series Analysis
	產品品質診斷
	機台預測性維護(predictive maintenance)

description.1086:
Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.
Corning succeeds through sustained investment in R&D, a unique combination of material and process innovation, and close collaboration with customers to solve tough technology challenges.
Corning’s Display Technologies segment manufactures glass substrates for active matrix liquid crystal displays (“LCDs”) that are used primarily in LCD televisions, notebook computers and flat panel desktop monitors.

Scope of Position:
- Primary function is to support research and development projects by developing and executing material characterization, process optimization, or/and new product application. The individual must have a solid technical background in Chemistry, Physics, or Material Science. Additionally, the individual is expected to have hands-on experiences in lab. In this role, the person will develop techniques and conduct experiments to address process issues if needed
- The individual will have the opportunity to be a member of cross-functional project sub-teams, on both early and late innovation stage projects, through concept generation / certification, technology development, detail design / build, and the installation into manufacturing

Key Responsibilities
- Interface and work with internal Research, Development and Manufacturing teams that are involved in the innovation process of new concepts and products
- Work with other project team members on understanding and solving project related issues, and general process engineering, and process understanding
- Utilize internal/external lab facilities and equipment to develop proof of concept prototypes
- Individual must be capable of executing project assignments with minimal supervision
- Ability to work in a team-based environment and participate on a highly matrixed project team
- Individual must investigate prior art and document any Intellectual Property developed as part of their project activities
- Individual must document project learning, progress, and results in technical reports
- Individual must present the project(s) they are involved with for review by peers and managers
- Characterize surfaces, morphologies, structures, and compositions of various samples using standard technologies
- Create presentations and analytical report to communicate with internal/external customers

description.1145:
Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.
Corning succeeds through sustained investment in R&D, a unique combination of material and process innovation, and close collaboration with customers to solve tough technology challenges.
Corning’s Display Technologies segment manufactures glass substrates for active matrix liquid crystal displays (“LCDs”) that are used primarily in LCD televisions, notebook computers and flat panel desktop monitors.

Purpose of the Position
• The qualified candidate will be mainly responsible for technical support of mechanical reliability and testing for Corning products, and collaboration with other subject matter experts not only as an individual contributor and also as a team. This role will provide project support at various stages of innovation, from early stage products to development, including the field support. Work with customers on understanding of the testing protocol and requirement for application need, and give feedback based on the testing and analysis result. Collaborate with other reliability experts, research teams and other internal resources to implement new characterization techniques based on customer requirements to improve product performance. This job will be fully supporting mechanical and reliability testing; however supporting other project-oriented activities/tasks may also be required.

Day to Day Responsibilities
• Support the daily operation of the mechanical testing lab and glass strengthening process need
• Design and conduct experiments for mechanical testing on glass as a component or within a device.
• Analyze results; document, communicate with internal & external customers, including formal presentation.
• Develop and improve experiment protocols 
• Support equipment qualification tests.
• Provide direct support to the existing Corning business in customers support and new platform business development.
• Support projects related to mechanical performance of glass and characterization; making recommendations to projects to improve functional performance and reliability
• Support to provide technical consultation and expertise to the commercial organization and/or directly with customers.

LSC Ecosystem (鄰近桃園機場捷運A7站) 的使命是在電動載具價值鏈上扮演關鍵領航者，你想對產業發揮自己的影響力嗎？在這裡你能夠有機會在電動載具的產業裡，串連軟體與硬體、協助傳統邁向未來，過程絕對不簡單，但是旅程保證很精彩。你喜歡新創充滿未知與挑戰的吸引力嗎？加入 LSC 和我們一起打造電動載具產業的霸業！


【Responsibilities】
• 開發基於 Artificial Intelligence / Machine Learning / Deep Learning 交通領域之演算法應用，建構研發期之雲端模型環境
• 將模型演算法優化於 Cloud Computing，提供 API 服務
• 與軟體部門與演算法工程師協作，確保將演算法模型導入雲端服務中


【Requirements】
• 資訊 / 電機等相關領域 M.S. 以上學位
• 需三年以上相關實務經驗
• 具任一雲端平台( AWS / GCP / Azure ) 演算法開發經驗者
• 熟悉Spark / Hadoop / MapReduce
• 具備高效率的Python / PySpark 編寫程式能力
• 具備資料工程 / ETL 之能力且具備版本控制工具經驗


【Preferred Skills】
• 能熟練操作 PostgreSQL 與 MongoDB
• 熟悉至少一種以上AI演算法。(ex: 推薦系統、深度學習、時間序列等)
• 熟悉 Linux 系統操作


【Special Requirement】
• 曾有實作經驗過車聯網雲端服務者佳
• 具備良好的閱讀國際期刊之能力
• 區塊鏈技術應用

description.1273:
仁寶電腦集團全球化運營與永續經營，持續追求成長與創新，積極進行數位化與AI人工智能轉型，延攬同時具備業界實務經驗與學術連結能力的AI人工智能專家。我們提供您在AI職涯發展上的3項資源與優勢：
1.應用場域與豐富數據：我們深信AI必須是從實務場域與數據中不斷學習淬煉，讓您能廣泛且持續鑽研企業完整價值鏈的作業與決策全歷程大數據；
2.實踐價值與創造生態：我們強調5E的歷程與結果「工程-演進-證據-體驗-生態」(Engineering-Evolution-Evidence-Experience-Ecosystem)，引領您親身經歷從「水平通用型AI」轉化為「垂直利基型AI」的實踐過程；
3.資源整合的連結平台：我們全力由R&D(Research & Development)邁向C&D(Connect & Development)，協助您快速有效連結三個層次的AI研發資源：全球智能、專案智能、與算法智能。

工作內容
1.與AI方案設計師合作，向價值鏈各領域決策/管理/現場人員交流學習，理解其組織願景/管理目標/作業流程/經驗法則/作業痛點/效能評估/價值定位/成就需求，共同討論並定義出能持續提升領域人員能力與附加價值的AI應用議題與對應技術。
2.以實際案例為基礎，與AI方案設計師及領域專家進行深入調研，充分掌握案例相關之人理/事理/物理，並收集散佈於相關資訊系統/人員/設備的案例過程全記錄數據，以確實理解案例現狀的決策歷程，並初步展現與評估AI應用於此案例的可行性與價值。
3.建立端對端(End-to-End) AI分析流程「數據收集-數據處理-特徵工程-模型訓練-模型推論-決策建議-人機協作-行動體驗-視覺呈現」的系統化工程與快速的POC(Proof of Concept)方案驗證。
4.與數據工程師合作，整合運用先進資訊技術/認知運算技術/物聯網技術，建立企業AI下水道工程，收集散佈於相關資訊系統/人員/設備的各類型大數據。
5.與平台工程師合作，將端對端資料分析流程與服務布建於分散式運算工業互聯網平台，達到分享重用、彈性組建、與運算資源動態優化的目的。
6.與設備(或辦公)自動化工程師合作，提供模型推論的運算服務，實現數據驅動機器人(或辦公代理人)的自動化(或人機協同)決策行動。
7.協同領域專家與AI方案設計師，系統化持續收集與整理實際發生案例，建立可分享重用的「案例庫/專家庫/知識庫/算法庫/模型庫」，不斷提升作業程序的整體效能與用戶體驗。

職能要求
1.傾聽：真誠傾聽、感受、與理解各領域人士經驗與需求，能體貼且持續耐心溝通，並且不畏困難，逐步釐清界定各議題核心的關鍵問題。
2.學習：「由外而內」廣泛連結與學習網路公開的AI資源，主動參與各種資料科學學會組織；「由內而外」深入持恆探究，不斷進行抽象化歸納/假設推理/決策驗證，持續形成對外溝通的各面向議題與對應解決方案之整體觀念架構。
3.卓越：勇於持續挑戰極致，以「提升客戶體驗」與「產生商業價值」為最高信念；深信數據是資產，不斷進行案例收集/深入解析/找出期望落差/提出對策方案/具體行動，進而形成自我驅動的閉環優化(closed-loop optimization)。
4.專業技能：
   (A) 具備統計分析與建模能力、且有3年以上的演算法設計與程式開發經驗；
   (B) 有機器學習與深度學習等相關應用開發經驗，如影像辨識/語音辨識/自然語言分析/語意理解/物聯網IoT時間序列分析等實作技術，並運用於智能製造/智能行銷/智能辦公等場域；
   (C) 能將資料分析流程與演算法進行系統化工程與表達，有效進行各模型版本的管理，並持續追蹤對應至各案例資料的效能表現。

#PowerApps/Power Automation

#We are looking to hire a skilled IDS support engineer to provide a solution based on PowerApps applications with Power Automate for employees’ productivity across our region. As an IT support engineer, he/she will closely work with IDS colleagues and if required based on the needs, can meet with end users to determine the nature of the problem, diagnose issues, provide effective assistance, and maintain strong relationships with end users.

Key Responsibilities:
To ensure success as an IDS support engineer for our region (Australia/NZ, Hong Kong, Korea and Taiwan), he/she needs to speak English, and have in depth knowledge of O365 apps, and excellent troubleshooting skills, high-level interpersonal skills and having curious on improving the current existing process. Ultimately a top-class IDS support engineer resolves all PowerApps/Power Automate issues quickly and effectively while maintaining a good relationship with key stakeholders.

• Meet with end users to diagnose the issue and pull the best solution
• Maintain a good relationship with end users
• Understand the business needs and quickly apply into the system
• Be creative on finding a solution to meet the expectation of business partners
• Even further can propose a better solution beyond the given fact/idea

description.1277:
▍關於偉康 Webcomm
　　WebComm 偉康科技股份有限公司成立於 1998 年，提供以人工智慧、數據應用、雲端運算服務及資訊安全等解決方案與系統建置服務，協助企業進行數位轉型並體現以消費者為導向的「數位科技生活圈」。
　　服務客戶不僅專注於金融科技 (Fin Tech)，橫跨公共服務、醫療照護、流通服務、電信媒體、科技製造等多元領域；更與業界巨人 ( IBM, Google, Red Hat, TIBCO, VMWare 等) 攜手同型，提供更完整專業的技術支援與服務。

▍工作內容
1. 針對數據應用系統進行 end-to-end 架構規劃。
2. 掌握及控制客戶需求與了解數據痛點，進行客戶需求訪談，進行需求確認，撰寫並經客戶確認需求規格書。
3. 數據架構設計：設計架構並協助專案經理評估各項需求所需開發時間及人力資源。
4. 數據系統設計：依據需求及整體系統架構，進行系統設計、資料庫模型設計、結構與運作方式，撰寫系統設計規格書。
5. 系統品質保證：撰寫整合測試計畫、審核系統整合測試報告及協助客戶進行 UAT 測試、撰寫系統壓力測試報告及記錄缺陷記錄表。

▍Must-have
1. 具專案所需程式設計 (python, java, nodejs) 及資料處理工具基礎。
2. 有數據專案或產品的架構設計實務經驗。
3. 熟悉 Agile、數據方法論及資料治理相關經驗。
4. 具有良好的溝通力、促成力與人際關係能力，熟練提問技巧，有效釐清客戶需求。

▍Nice to have
1. 樂觀、積極的工作態度。
2. 具有良好的創造力能轉化使用者業務需求成系統的功能與非功能需求的能力。
3. 需具備能從客戶身上快速學習與吸收領域知識的能力。
4. 具有良好分析力，要能拆解並找出基本元素及其結構相依性與因果關係。

● 91APP 提供什麼樣的服務？ 
91APP 提供品牌與零售業者全通路新零售解決方案，協助客戶以會員為核心、全通路經營，進行數據驅動的智慧銷售，促進會員在線上與門市的消費循環，實現 OMO 虛實融合，帶動零售行業升級。

● 具體工作內容
從產品、銷售等層面建構完整的數據分析體系，並通過數據探索、各案分析等應用，提供產品、營運決策有質量的數據支持。

• 數據專案 – 參與產品專案中與數據相關的議題，協助定義數據收集與後續分析需求，規劃並推動數據產品，推動公司朝向數據驅動營運的實現。

• 數據分析 – 主動進行各種數據追蹤和分析，針對商業問題提出數據產出、評估與應用，並持續優化與修正。建立全面、準確的經營管理成效衡量指標，幫助電商洞察經營數據，提供有效的決策支援。

一、統整及管理企業內部數據應用需求，並轉化為開發/系統規格
1. 與RD協作設計企業應用資料庫(含CRM、產品DB、訂單DB等等)，追蹤並管理RD資料探勘、處理、分析、匯總的架構設計
2. 接收內部數據分析需求，執行分析工作，產出結論與洞見
3. 負責內部同仁日常營運所需之數據分析工具教育訓練
4. 管理數據分析/資料處理相關的專案，需熟練跨部門溝通&協作

二、依循數據驅動設計，負責智生活產品潛在商機及解決方案的應用分析及判讀
1.依據團隊客戶行為分析、畫像(persona)描繪，進行解釋與預測，並撰寫分析報告(如預測趨勢或客戶行為)，並設計Pesona分群貼標與應用評估架構。

職務需求
【必備條件】
1.高度數據導向，擅長透過數據分析解讀，優化商業營運績效。
2.熟悉資料庫、特徵工程、機器學習，以及大數據架構與經驗佳
3.主動積極，抗壓性高，團隊配合度高，具資料可視化及簡報能力
4.良好的溝通協調能力，整合公司產品、設計、市場團隊等各方面資源，進行有效溝通。
5. 具備向上、水平管理之能力，邏輯清晰面對需求能夠迅速分析，找出最佳解決方案。
6. 具備自主學習能力，面對問題及挑戰能自行在專業能力定期精進及成長，成為團隊成長的動能

【加分條件】
1.資料科學/數據分析/資料工程相關經驗
2.具SQL資料庫程式撰寫能力
3.具Python資料分析及資料工程程式能力

【工作文化】
目標導向、敏捷迭代
所有功能開發及決策都是為了追求的是具體成效，例如收益增加多少，點擊率提升多少，並透過規劃及執行的持續迭代，直到目的達成為止。
當責文化、自主決策
你將需要協助團隊做出對公司最好的決策，並爭取公司資源投入你的專案，可行性評估包括事前的相關數據搜集分析、風險評估、利益關係人分析。
年輕開放、高成長性
設計團隊年輕，彼此可以獨立作業，也可以相互支持，具有活潑、熱情的工作氛圍。

如果你符合以下特質，請盡快與我們聯繫
1、熱衷於設計真正有價值的商業模式或服務
2、勇於挑戰，不怕失敗，只怕沒機會嘗試
3、不受限既有的思維模式，勇於帶領自己與他人突破與創新
4、解決顧客問題，為顧客創造WOW的使用體驗會讓你感到非常有成就感
5、兼具理性與感性，能夠理性的產品設計與資訊架構，也能創造感性的顧客體驗
6、樂與分享，願意接納別人想法，同時透過回饋想法跟意見，讓產品變得更好

description.1389:
我們正在尋找數據分析師加入我們的數據團隊。您將負責管理我們的主數據集，開發報告以及對數據問題進行假設與實驗。為了出色地履行這一職責，您需要非常對細節有所堅持、對於數據分析工具和資料庫有深刻理解。

工作職責：
1. 管理數據，包括創建，更新和刪除。。
2. 導入數據驅動決策相關分析，必要時需要跨部門合作。
3. 調試和停用數據集。
4. 根據準則處理機密數據和資訊。
5. 幫助開發報告和分析。

8. 配合數據完整性和標準化的計劃。

10. 從單個或多個系統生成報告。
11. 對報告數據庫環境和報告進行故障排除。
12. 評估資料分析系統的更改和更新。

5. 能夠將業務需求轉換為非技術性的非專業術語。

8. 了解元數據標準。
9. 高水平的書面和口頭交流能力。
10. 至少需要擅長一種數據分析語言, ex. R, SQL, Python等

description.1539:
Scope of Position
Qualified candidates will be mainly responsible for the development of radar algorithms and vehicle application systems for Qianjun products, including blind spot recognition and alarm strategies for radar sensors, and work with experts from other departments as independent researchers and teams.

1. Develop and design based on the currently developed tracking algorithm to integrate ADAS application specifications.
2. Work with customers to understand the causes of abnormal radar alarms, and analyze and propose solutions from the perspective of algorithms. Cooperate with other experts throughout Qianjun.
3. Strong technical curiosity, will provide unique solutions to technical challenges.
4. Ability to work in a team-based environment and participate in a matrix project team.

Day to Day Responsibilities
(1) Familiar with and understand the operation process of 77GHz FMCW radar.
(2) Understand the regulatory requirements in the application context, and design application algorithms based on this requirement.
(3) Understand and participate in the development and design of radar tracking systems.
(4) Use git version management tools.
(5) Conduct experiment records and performance analysis to ensure that the system is stable and there is no risk of crash.
(6) Proactively report work progress and have a good team spirit.
(7) Good problem analysis ability and propose appropriate solutions.

-熟悉且了解77G毫米波雷達工作原理。
-基於目前開發的追蹤算法，開發/維護車用雷達應用算法(BSD、LCA、RCTA、SBZA、RCW、FCW等)。
-演算法參數優化。
-參與演算法評估分析、雷達規格評估。
-與團隊/客戶一同了解雷達異常報警的原因，從算法的角度分析並提出解決方案。

• 通過使用Google Analytics等分析工具，提供網站分析服務，包括規劃、操作和其他運營過程中的咨詢服務。

• 獲取並分析廣告資料，對異常資料進行分析和排查，保障線上廣告正常提供服務；

description.1558:
【公司部門簡介 About us】
國泰金控為臺灣服務客戶數最多的領先金融服務業者，致力於成為亞洲最佳金融機構。旗下的國泰世華銀行，為全臺灣數位服務用戶數的領先銀行，其數位銀行部更是國泰金控數位轉型之重要推動引擎，致力於打造優質、創新的數位金融服務。部門團隊由各領域菁英所組成，成員背景多元，橫跨金融產業、管理顧問、網路科技、時尚旅遊、數位行銷及新創科技等各領域。你將有機會與頂尖人才共事，共同實現數位新世代前所未有的可能。我們廣納優秀的專業人才，也打造開放溝通的工作環境。我們相信，唯有在開放式的團隊文化，才激得起最熱烈的革命火花。

金融科技已在改變世界，加入國泰世華銀行，你將有機會改變臺灣金融發展史。

【主要職責 Who we are looking for】
擅於洞察多元數據、分析客戶行為，協助商業決策、商機探索，持續帶入創新洞見提升數位經營效益的人才。

【職務說明 What will you do】
1.	撰寫 SQL 分析資料，使用Tableau, Google Analytics等數位工具分析用戶行為並將資料視覺化。
2.	解析客群數位行為、跨平台經營數據，並提出洞察、建議改善與發展方向。
3.	追蹤與分析各產品行銷活動之分群回應率與經營成效。

【發展與培訓 Development & training】 
這是一項非常具挑戰性的工作，因此我們會盡全力支援你在各工作階段的發展。從你加入的第一天起，我們將提供全方位的集團培訓計畫。首先你會得到產品知識訓練；並對於想深入了解的領域，可根據需求報名集團與知名企業合作，所提供的數位行銷、分析、使用者體驗等相關課程，形式包含定期系列講座、實戰工作坊。若這些課程無法滿足你的需求，也可自由選擇申請外部進修補助，並有機會得到全額進修補助。此外，你也能接觸不同業務部門，更深入至有興趣的專業領域工作。

91APP 提供品牌與零售業者全通路新零售解決方案，協助客戶以會員為核心、全通路經營，進行數據驅動的智慧銷售，促進會員在線上與門市的消費循環，實現 OMO 虛實融合，帶動零售行業升級。

工作內容：
處理及分析生醫大數據，如多體學基因體、環境空污及健保資料庫資料，探討基因與空污(如PM2.5)對疾病的影響，串接健保資料庫及環境資料探討環境對疾病發生率的影響，以機器學習演算法(random forest、SVM等)及深度學習模型(deep neural network、CNN、RNN等)建置疾病預測模型。

本研究室提供內部及外部教育訓練機會，如內部讀書會、國家高速網路中心提供的機器學習法及類神經網路在大數據的應用等。關於本研究室的研究方向及成員可參考: http://rclab.nhri.org.tw

應徵條件：
1. 統計或資訊相關系所大學以上學歷
2. 對生醫大數據研究有興趣
3. 熟悉R或Python

工作待遇：
學士33000以上，碩士38000以上

description.1805:
英文能力需為native speaker等級

Purpose of the job: 

Digital Domain, is a creative force which has brought artistry and technology to hundreds of motion pictures, commercials and games through its groundbreaking visual effects.  Some of its latest technology  can be seen at work in films such as  Avengers: Infinity War, Ready Player One, Fast 8,  Spiderman, Beauty and The Beast. 

We are seeking a technology lead to join a high level R&D team of software engineers, TDs and artists focused on developing new technology to generate photorealistic, live, real-time, performing digital humans and creatures.  The technology we are developing spans the gamut from machine learning to computer graphics to computer vision and real-time game platforms. This diverse project is in need of a technical manager to deal with day management of the developers, maintaining a development schedule, leading the various teams and more. 

This will be a hands on role, we expect the ideal candidate to do development, be able to run the software we have developed and guide the developers towards solutions. This is a complex project; it combines serious research and development and the difficulties of managing that but also the need to build working tools that will scale. 

The ideal candidate will have an understanding of building tools that use machine learning, knowledge of developing real-time applications, an understanding of cloud-based computing and has taken products to market before. Past work in a visual effects or gaming environment is a plus. 

The candidate will work out of the DD Taiwan office overseeing engineers there but also working with the teams in LA and BC.


Essential Functions/Responsibilities:

●	Lead and work with a software team that is creating new tools for artists and users based on the latest research. 
●	Schedule and manage the team of developers.
●	Manage the computing resources needed and develop cloud-based approaches that will scale with our expected growth. 
●	Have regular meetings with the leadership of this team and with the developers. 
●	Travel between Taiwan, China, Los Angeles and Vancouver is possible.
●	Must be fluent in English and Mandarian.

descSnippet.1:
Why Verifone

For more than 30 years VeriFone has established a remarkable record of leadership in the electronic payment technology industry. VeriFone has one of the leading electronic payment solutions brands and is one of the largest providers of electronic payment systems worldwide.

VeriFone has a diverse, dynamic, and fast-paced work environment in which employees are focused on results and have opportunities to excel. We take pride in the fact that we work with the best and brightest in our industry around the globe. Our competitive fierceness is fed by our passion for excellence in our products and services, and our obsession with customer satisfaction. Across the globe, VeriFone employees are leading the payments industry through experience, innovation, and an entrepreneurial spirit. Whether it’s developing the next platform of secure payment systems or searching for new ways to bring electronic payments to new markets, the team at VeriFone is dedicated to the success of our customers, partners, and investors. It's this passion for innovation that drives each one of our employees to personal and professional success.

What you'll do
Position Summary:

Seek a senior hardware engineer to perform board-level circuit design and development, including digital, analog, and power system management technologies. Determine design approaches and parameters. Conduct experimental tests and analyze operating data to contribute to the development schedule.

Essential Duties and Responsibilities:

• Perform board-level circuit design and development, including digital, analog, and/or system power portions. 
• Responsible for parts selection, schematic capture, and BOM maintenance. 
• Responsible for the design and development of new products as well as the support and modification of existing products. 
• Documentation of design files and theory of operation. 
• Board level debug and field returned failure analysis.
• EMC debug to comply with CE/FCC standard. 
• May lead development projects.

What qualifications will you need to be successful?
Knowledge & Experience:

• Preferred master's degree in Electrical Engineering in a related field with 4 or more years of a hardware design engineer. 
• Knowledge of embedded system design and hardware components such as Signal Integrity design and validation, ARM-based chipsets, Touch Screen display, System Power design, especially with analog circuit design ability. 
• Understanding of various communication channels, including but not limited to RS232, USB, Ethernet, SPI, I2C, I2S, and SDIO. 
• System design with ARM CPU and related interfacing. 
• Experience designing cost-effective PCBA's for embedded systems products. 
• Good verbal and written communications skills. 
• Ability to effectively handle multiple tasks. 
• Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, including failure analysis.

Our commitment

Verifone is committed to creating a diverse environment and is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, gender, gender, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, national origin, genetics, disability, age, or veteran status. Verifone is also committed to compliance with all fair employment practices regarding citizenship and immigration status.

descSnippet.4:
We are looking forward to building a team of Sr. and Jr. Embedded SW Engineer to execute complete embedded software development life cycle. The goal is to create scalable and optimized system solution with our MCU/DSP/ADC IP.

College graduates with related field are welcome!!!

We offer 14 months guaranteed pay with Health and Labour insurance. Company stocks and many more! Come and join us! 

Embedded Software Engineer responsibilities include:
• Designing and implementing software of embedded devices and systems
• Designing, developing, coding, testing and debugging system software
• Analyzing and enhancing efficiency, stability and scalability of system resources


Responsibilities
• Design and implement software of embedded devices and systems from requirements to production and commercial deployment
• Design, develop, code, test and debug system software
• Review code and design
• Analyze and enhance efficiency, stability and scalability of system resources
• Integrate and validate new product designs
• Support software QA and optimize I/O performance
• Provide post production support
• Interface with hardware design and development
• Assess third party and open source software

Requirements
• Proven working experience in software engineering
• BS degree in Computer Science or Engineering
• Experience in hands-on development and troubleshooting on embedded 
targets
• Solid programming experience in C or C++
• Proven experience in embedded systems design with preemptive, multitasking real-time operating systems
• Familiarity with software configuration management tools, defect tracking tools, and peer review
• Excellent knowledge of OS coding techniques, IP protocols, interfaces and hardware subsystems
• Adequate knowledge of reading schematics and data sheets for components
• Strong documentation, writing  and communication skills
descSnippet.5:

【About the Role】
As a Customer Service Representative, you will be participating in customer service training programs and being led by senior colleagues to accumulate practical experience. You will assist the company in observing the behaviors and feedbacks of teachers and students on the platform, patiently putting yourself in customer's position to communicate and convey the core values of AmazingTalker.
The customer service team has to process hundreds of and thousands of messages every day, so you will need to prioritize your to-dos to properly arrange limited resources and time. At the same time, you will also need to have a keen sense of observation in order to find the problem in the user's narrative. In addition, you will use data analysis to collect user feedback, cooperate with the product optimization team, make suggestions, conduct research and implement, ultimately optimizing the product to fundamentally solve the user's problem. Most importantly, you will also need to optimize existing processes and establish standard operation procedures, so that repetitive tasks can be completed in a more efficient manner.

descSnippet.92:
Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.
Corning succeeds through sustained investment in R&D, a unique combination of material and process innovation, and close collaboration with customers to solve tough technology challenges.
Corning’s Display Technologies segment manufactures glass substrates for active matrix liquid crystal displays (“LCDs”) that are used primarily in LCD televisions, notebook computers and flat panel desktop monitors.

Scope of Position:
We are offering a unique job opportunity to conduct cutting-edge research in an exciting field of NLP (English). This job provides a wide range of opportunities to invent and to bring fruition to new life-changing technologies with NLP machine/deep learning (ML/DL) capability.

The successful candidate will
• Work from the Corning Research Center Taiwan located inside ITRI (Industrial Technology Research Institute) in Hsinchu and closely interact with other Corning R&D teams around the globe
• Provide technical leadership for research projects and activities focusing on NLP to support Corning RD&E
• Require proven hands-on experience training and optimizing models, building production-ready inference pipelines in Python
• Guide efforts for developing novel NLP models for Corning businesses
• Play a leading role in creation of relevant IP to protect key inventions related to novel solutions

Day to Day Responsibilities:
• Propose and lead research activities involving NLP evaluation and customization for different applications across Corning businesses; be responsible to understand problems from the customer's point of view and translate into NLP solution and work plans
• Collaborate with internal customers across Corning organizations, design and perform model validation and testing, communicate technical practices and results to internal customers
• Share and contribute Corning’s NLP community of practice in developing the capabilities and promoting areas of applications
• Release and maintain developed code for research and creative tools
• Around 15% global travel is expected

descSnippet.127:
大數據分析已成為企業競爭力的重要關鍵之一，其中人工智慧(Artificial Intelligence)被視為是翻轉產業的革命型技術。台達電子為了加速產業界導入AI應用，創造智慧化的加值服務，整合AI相關技術與培訓資源，因而成立AI創新中心(AI Center of Excellence)。 
因應瞬息萬變的商業環境，共享與協作才能快速創新，這是AI創新中心在資源及服務上的定位，台達將透過此中心的資源來培訓人才並與各事業單位合作，落實AI技術於各式服務。

本職缺主要工作內容:
1.	以統計、訊號處理、機器學習與深度學習等技術，透過內外部客戶建立合適的分析診斷解決方案
2.	研究與開發人工智慧之演算法、應用和服務
3.	設計、協助及管理資料分析及最佳化專案、培訓等業務推動
4.	參與智慧製造、智慧生活、智慧企業等產業轉型專案，並設計開發分析流程(含資料採集、邊緣運算分流、演算法選用等)。

你/妳將會應用資料分析技術於以下兩大類別問題
1.	Video & Image Processing and Analytics
	缺陷檢測
	缺陷分類
2.	Time Series Analysis
	產品品質診斷
	機台預測性維護(predictive maintenance)
	傳感器訊號融合分析
	訊號降噪/濾波/萃取等演算法開發

Scope:
In this position you will lead product and process development projects for Linde Electronics. You will be in the Linde Asia Electronics Specialty Gases/Advanced Materials R&D and Applications team, headquartered at the Linde Electronics Research and Development Center (ERDC) in Taichung, Taiwan.

You will engage and collaborate with Linde’s international R&D colleagues, regional businesses, and suppliers to develop and commercialize new products, including novel chemistries, purification technologies and packaging/delivery systems for the Electronics market.

Duties and Responsibilities:
•	Plan and execute R&D experimental lab programs for high-value products safely, on time and on budget.  Lead technical deliverables specification and proof-of-concept demonstration, including but not limited to:
- Experimental system design that is ready for scale up
- System build
- System de-commission
- Initial process design in conjunction with other team members
- Liaison with equipment and raw material vendors for pricing options

•	Activities will encompass all aspects of the development system design and operation such as:
- Adsorption bed sizing
- Adsorption bed breakthrough testing
- Heat exchanger design
- Reactor heating/cooling calculations
- Distillation column sizing
- Distillation physical property verifications
- Adsorption column /scrubber column sizing
- Synthesis reactor sizing
- Materials compatibility
- Dilution and purge calculations

Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.
Corning succeeds through sustained investment in R&D, a unique combination of material and process innovation, and close collaboration with customers to solve tough technology challenges.
Corning’s Display Technologies segment manufactures glass substrates for active matrix liquid crystal displays (“LCDs”) that are used primarily in LCD televisions, notebook computers and flat panel desktop monitors.

Scope of Position:
- Primary function is to support research and development projects by developing and executing material characterization, process optimization, or/and new product application. The individual must have a solid technical background in Chemistry, Physics, or Material Science. Additionally, the individual is expected to have hands-on experiences in lab. In this role, the person will develop techniques and conduct experiments to address process issues if needed
- The individual will have the opportunity to be a member of cross-functional project sub-teams, on both early and late innovation stage projects, through concept generation / certification, technology development, detail design / build, and the installation into manufacturing

Key Responsibilities
- Interface and work with internal Research, Development and Manufacturing teams that are involved in the innovation process of new concepts and products
- Work with other project team members on understanding and solving project related issues, and general process engineering, and process understanding
- Utilize internal/external lab facilities and equipment to develop proof of concept prototypes
- Individual must be capable of executing project assignments with minimal supervision
- Ability to work in a team-based environment and participate on a highly matrixed project team
- Individual must investigate prior art and document any Intellectual Property developed as part of their project activities
- Individual must document project learning, progress, and results in technical reports
- Individual must present the project(s) they are involved with for review by peers and managers
- Characterize surfaces, morphologies, structures, and compositions of various samples using standard technologies
- Create presentations and analytical report to communicate with internal/external customers

Corning is one of the world’s leading innovators in materials science. For more than 160 years, Corning has applied its unparalleled expertise in specialty glass, ceramics, and optical physics to develop products that have created new industries and transformed people’s lives.

Purpose of the Position
• The qualified candidate will be mainly responsible for technical support of mechanical reliability and testing for Corning products, and collaboration with other subject matter experts not only as an individual contributor and also as a team. This role will provide project support at various stages of innovation, from early stage products to development, including the field support. Work with customers on understanding of the testing protocol and requirement for application need, and give feedback based on the testing and analysis result. Collaborate with other reliability experts, research teams and other internal resources to implement new characterization techniques based on customer requirements to improve product performance. This job will be fully supporting mechanical and reliability testing; however supporting other project-oriented activities/tasks may also be required.

• Support the daily operation of the mechanical testing lab and glass strengthening process need

• Develop and improve experiment protocols 
• Support equipment qualification tests.
• Provide direct support to the existing Corning business in customers support and new platform business development.
• Support projects related to mechanical performance of glass and characterization; making recommendations to projects to improve functional performance and reliability
• Support to provide technical consultation and expertise to the commercial organization and/or directly with customers.

descSnippet.1273:
仁寶電腦集團全球化運營與永續經營，持續追求成長與創新，積極進行數位化與AI人工智能轉型，延攬同時具備業界實務經驗與學術連結能力的AI人工智能專家。我們提供您在AI職涯發展上的3項資源與優勢：
1.應用場域與豐富數據：我們深信AI必須是從實務場域與數據中不斷學習淬煉，讓您能廣泛且持續鑽研企業完整價值鏈的作業與決策全歷程大數據；
2.實踐價值與創造生態：我們強調5E的歷程與結果「工程-演進-證據-體驗-生態」(Engineering-Evolution-Evidence-Experience-Ecosystem)，引領您親身經歷從「水平通用型AI」轉化為「垂直利基型AI」的實踐過程；
3.資源整合的連結平台：我們全力由R&D(Research & Development)邁向C&D(Connect & Development)，協助您快速有效連結三個層次的AI研發資源：全球智能、專案智能、與算法智能。

工作內容
1.與AI方案設計師合作，向價值鏈各領域決策/管理/現場人員交流學習，理解其組織願景/管理目標/作業流程/經驗法則/作業痛點/效能評估/價值定位/成就需求，共同討論並定義出能持續提升領域人員能力與附加價值的AI應用議題與對應技術。
2.以實際案例為基礎，與AI方案設計師及領域專家進行深入調研，充分掌握案例相關之人理/事理/物理，並收集散佈於相關資訊系統/人員/設備的案例過程全記錄數據，以確實理解案例現狀的決策歷程，並初步展現與評估AI應用於此案例的可行性與價值。
3.建立端對端(End-to-End) AI分析流程「數據收集-數據處理-特徵工程-模型訓練-模型推論-決策建議-人機協作-行動體驗-視覺呈現」的系統化工程與快速的POC(Proof of Concept)方案驗證。
4.與數據工程師合作，整合運用先進資訊技術/認知運算技術/物聯網技術，建立企業AI下水道工程，收集散佈於相關資訊系統/人員/設備的各類型大數據。
5.與平台工程師合作，將端對端資料分析流程與服務布建於分散式運算工業互聯網平台，達到分享重用、彈性組建、與運算資源動態優化的目的。
6.與設備(或辦公)自動化工程師合作，提供模型推論的運算服務，實現數據驅動機器人(或辦公代理人)的自動化(或人機協同)決策行動。
7.協同領域專家與AI方案設計師，系統化持續收集與整理實際發生案例，建立可分享重用的「案例庫/專家庫/知識庫/算法庫/模型庫」，不斷提升作業程序的整體效能與用戶體驗。

職能要求
1.傾聽：真誠傾聽、感受、與理解各領域人士經驗與需求，能體貼且持續耐心溝通，並且不畏困難，逐步釐清界定各議題核心的關鍵問題。
2.學習：「由外而內」廣泛連結與學習網路公開的AI資源，主動參與各種資料科學學會組織；「由內而外」深入持恆探究，不斷進行抽象化歸納/假設推理/決策驗證，持續形成對外溝通的各面向議題與對應解決方案之整體觀念架構。
3.卓越：勇於持續挑戰極致，以「提升客戶體驗」與「產生商業價值」為最高信念；深信數據是資產，不斷進行案例收集/深入解析/找出期望落差/提出對策方案/具體行動，進而形成自我驅動的閉環優化(closed-loop optimization)。
4.專業技能：
   (A) 具備統計分析與建模能力、且有3年以上的演算法設計與程式開發經驗；
   (B) 有機器學習與深度學習等相關應用開發經驗，如影像辨識/語音辨識/自然語言分析/語意理解/物聯網IoT時間序列分析等實作技術，並運用於智能製造/智能行銷/智能辦公等場域；
   (C) 能將資料分析流程與演算法進行系統化工程與表達，有效進行各模型版本的管理，並持續追蹤對應至各案例資料的效能表現。

descSnippet.1344:
● 91APP 提供什麼樣的服務？ 
91APP 提供品牌與零售業者全通路新零售解決方案，協助客戶以會員為核心、全通路經營，進行數據驅動的智慧銷售，促進會員在線上與門市的消費循環，實現 OMO 虛實融合，帶動零售行業升級。

● 具體工作內容
從產品、銷售等層面建構完整的數據分析體系，並通過數據探索、各案分析等應用，提供產品、營運決策有質量的數據支持。

• 數據專案 – 參與產品專案中與數據相關的議題，協助定義數據收集與後續分析需求，規劃並推動數據產品，推動公司朝向數據驅動營運的實現。
• 數據模型 – 依據資料演算與分析需求，建構所需要的資料處理流程與數據模型，根據實際業務調整資料模型與 ETL 流程。
• 數據工程 – 能善用自動化的方法處理資料，熟悉大量資料處理與分析，使數據分析與應用產品化。
• 數據分析 – 主動進行各種數據追蹤和分析，針對商業問題提出數據產出、評估與應用，並持續優化與修正。建立全面、準確的經營管理成效衡量指標，幫助電商洞察經營數據，提供有效的決策支援。

● 團隊價值觀與文化 
1. 擁抱變化：能夠認同公司在快速發展之下的所有變化，包括產品發展方向、組織調整，快速地進行自我調適。 
2. 務實主義：開放地面對問題，從真實場景洞察與定義需求，也鼓勵聚焦目標的方案思辯，解決真實的問題，共創更好的產品服務。 
3. 價值論述與結果導向：能從客戶、公司、團隊的角度去論述價值，並且用具體的行動創造商業影響，以終為始地推動產品發展。

【必備條件】
1.高度數據導向，擅長透過數據分析解讀，優化商業營運績效。

【工作文化】
目標導向、敏捷迭代
所有功能開發及決策都是為了追求的是具體成效，例如收益增加多少，點擊率提升多少，並透過規劃及執行的持續迭代，直到目的達成為止。

年輕開放、高成長性
設計團隊年輕，彼此可以獨立作業，也可以相互支持，具有活潑、熱情的工作氛圍。

如果你符合以下特質，請盡快與我們聯繫
1、熱衷於設計真正有價值的商業模式或服務

descSnippet.1389:
我們正在尋找數據分析師加入我們的數據團隊。您將負責管理我們的主數據集，開發報告以及對數據問題進行假設與實驗。為了出色地履行這一職責，您需要非常對細節有所堅持、對於數據分析工具和資料庫有深刻理解。

工作職責：
1. 管理數據，包括創建，更新和刪除。。
2. 導入數據驅動決策相關分析，必要時需要跨部門合作。
3. 調試和停用數據集。
4. 根據準則處理機密數據和資訊。
5. 幫助開發報告和分析。 
6. 管理和設計報告環境，包括數據源，安全性和元數據。
7. 配合數據倉庫識別和修訂報告要求。
8. 配合數據完整性和標準化的計劃。
9. 評估測試並實施新的或升級的軟件。
10. 從單個或多個系統生成報告。
11. 對報告數據庫環境和報告進行故障排除。
12. 評估資料分析系統的更改和更新。
13. 在新報告和儀表板上對內部員工進行教育訓練。
14. 提供有關數據存儲結構，數據挖掘和數據清理的技術專長。
15. 提供各單位業務相關數據撈取工具與報表。

數據分析師要求：
1. 擁有資工、統計、數學等領域大學或以上學位。
2. 作為數據分析師或相關領域的工作經驗2年以上工作經驗，或相關領域碩士學歷。
3. 與產品經理共事以評估潛在風險的能力。
4. 能夠利用現有工具和數據庫進行分析，並提供應用軟體相關解決方案建議。
5. 能夠將業務需求轉換為非技術性的非專業術語。
6. 精熟於管理大型資料庫的方法與流程。
7. 在處理大型數據集和關聯式資料庫方面具有豐富的經驗。
8. 了解元數據標準。
9. 高水平的書面和口頭交流能力。
10. 至少需要擅長一種數據分析語言, ex. R, SQL, Python等
11. 至少需要精熟一種圖形化分析工具, ex. Tableau, Excel, GA
12. 對於AI、ML等開發運用有經驗者，加分。
13. 有成功的GA商業營用經驗者，加分。
14. 有博弈產業經驗者，加分。
15. 有BigQuery等雲端大數據分析經驗者，加分。

公司福利基於法定勞基法之上，該有的都有且優於，若您覺得還不足，也歡迎靠自己實力與付出爭取。

Scope of Position
Qualified candidates will be mainly responsible for the development of radar algorithms and vehicle application systems for Qianjun products, including blind spot recognition and alarm strategies for radar sensors, and work with experts from other departments as independent researchers and teams.

1. Develop and design based on the currently developed tracking algorithm to integrate ADAS application specifications.
2. Work with customers to understand the causes of abnormal radar alarms, and analyze and propose solutions from the perspective of algorithms. Cooperate with other experts throughout Qianjun.
3. Strong technical curiosity, will provide unique solutions to technical challenges.
4. Ability to work in a team-based environment and participate in a matrix project team.

Day to Day Responsibilities
(1) Familiar with and understand the operation process of 77GHz FMCW radar.
(2) Understand the regulatory requirements in the application context, and design application algorithms based on this requirement.
(3) Understand and participate in the development and design of radar tracking systems.
(4) Use git version management tools.
(5) Conduct experiment records and performance analysis to ensure that the system is stable and there is no risk of crash.
(6) Proactively report work progress and have a good team spirit.
(7) Good problem analysis ability and propose appropriate solutions.

【公司部門簡介 About us】
國泰金控為臺灣服務客戶數最多的領先金融服務業者，致力於成為亞洲最佳金融機構。旗下的國泰世華銀行，為全臺灣數位服務用戶數的領先銀行，其數位銀行部更是國泰金控數位轉型之重要推動引擎，致力於打造優質、創新的數位金融服務。部門團隊由各領域菁英所組成，成員背景多元，橫跨金融產業、管理顧問、網路科技、時尚旅遊、數位行銷及新創科技等各領域。你將有機會與頂尖人才共事，共同實現數位新世代前所未有的可能。我們廣納優秀的專業人才，也打造開放溝通的工作環境。我們相信，唯有在開放式的團隊文化，才激得起最熱烈的革命火花。

金融科技已在改變世界，加入國泰世華銀行，你將有機會改變臺灣金融發展史。

【主要職責 Who we are looking for】
擅於洞察多元數據、分析客戶行為，協助商業決策、商機探索，持續帶入創新洞見提升數位經營效益的人才。

【職務說明 What will you do】
1.	撰寫 SQL 分析資料，使用Tableau, Google Analytics等數位工具分析用戶行為並將資料視覺化。
2.	解析客群數位行為、跨平台經營數據，並提出洞察、建議改善與發展方向。
3.	追蹤與分析各產品行銷活動之分群回應率與經營成效。

【發展與培訓 Development & training】 
這是一項非常具挑戰性的工作，因此我們會盡全力支援你在各工作階段的發展。從你加入的第一天起，我們將提供全方位的集團培訓計畫。首先你會得到產品知識訓練；並對於想深入了解的領域，可根據需求報名集團與知名企業合作，所提供的數位行銷、分析、使用者體驗等相關課程，形式包含定期系列講座、實戰工作坊。若這些課程無法滿足你的需求，也可自由選擇申請外部進修補助，並有機會得到全額進修補助。此外，你也能接觸不同業務部門，更深入至有興趣的專業領域工作。

91APP 提供品牌與零售業者全通路新零售解決方案，協助客戶以會員為核心、全通路經營，進行數據驅動的智慧銷售，促進會員在線上與門市的消費循環，實現 OMO 虛實融合，帶動零售行業升級。

工作內容：
處理及分析生醫大數據，如多體學基因體、環境空污及健保資料庫資料，探討基因與空污(如PM2.5)對疾病的影響，串接健保資料庫及環境資料探討環境對疾病發生率的影響，以機器學習演算法(random forest、SVM等)及深度學習模型(deep neural network、CNN、RNN等)建置疾病預測模型。

本研究室提供內部及外部教育訓練機會，如內部讀書會、國家高速網路中心提供的機器學習法及類神經網路在大數據的應用等。關於本研究室的研究方向及成員可參考: http://rclab.nhri.org.tw

Purpose of the job: 

Digital Domain, is a creative force which has brought artistry and technology to hundreds of motion pictures, commercials and games through its groundbreaking visual effects.  Some of its latest technology  can be seen at work in films such as  Avengers: Infinity War, Ready Player One, Fast 8,  Spiderman, Beauty and The Beast. 

We are seeking a technology lead to join a high level R&D team of software engineers, TDs and artists focused on developing new technology to generate photorealistic, live, real-time, performing digital humans and creatures.  The technology we are developing spans the gamut from machine learning to computer graphics to computer vision and real-time game platforms. This diverse project is in need of a technical manager to deal with day management of the developers, maintaining a development schedule, leading the various teams and more. 

This will be a hands on role, we expect the ideal candidate to do development, be able to run the software we have developed and guide the developers towards solutions. This is a complex project; it combines serious research and development and the difficulties of managing that but also the need to build working tools that will scale. 

The ideal candidate will have an understanding of building tools that use machine learning, knowledge of developing real-time applications, an understanding of cloud-based computing and has taken products to market before. Past work in a visual effects or gaming environment is a plus. 

The candidate will work out of the DD Taiwan office overseeing engineers there but also working with the teams in LA and BC.


Essential Functions/Responsibilities:

●	Lead and work with a software team that is creating new tools for artists and users based on the latest research. 
●	Schedule and manage the team of developers.
●	Manage the computing resources needed and develop cloud-based approaches that will scale with our expected growth. 
●	Have regular meetings with the leadership of this team and with the developers. 
●	Travel between Taiwan, China, Los Angeles and Vancouver is possible.
●	Must be fluent in English and Mandarian.

descSnippet.1916:
關於Playsee:
Playsee是一個以影片分享為主的地緣性社群平台，讓用戶可以盡情地探索世界。我們不僅擁有兩千萬下載量，也數次獲得Google Play Store全球排行榜Top 10的殊榮。

我們是一群懷抱夢想的熱血青年，在開放式空間一起工作，在歡樂的氛圍中激盪新點子，創意發想解決問題的方案。

身為iOS開發工程師，你將為所有Apple用戶開發Playsee平台。肩負擁有上百萬用戶的應用程式的重任，你必須對手機介面有透徹的了解。

4.分析並優化app的表現及效能
 
以專業角度來說，這會是你勝任此職務的必要條件：
1. 需具備3年以上相關經驗
2. 熟悉使用Restful API和parsing JSON

4. 熟悉Objective-C 或是swift
